{"tid":1649221,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國際民調: 中國的受歡迎程度大減","createTime":"2019-10-12T14:26:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T16:23:55.000Z","uid":134071,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1190f3d4e1eeb0c27a1538469b37894572eb8110","tid":1649221,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:26:17.000Z","msg":"中國在全球多個主要國家的受歡迎程度都大減.... 但俄羅斯人卻反而更喜歡中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.storm.mg/lifestyle/1797528\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.storm.mg%2Flifestyle%2F1797528&d=NX17wA0xajt0Xz52GN5L9goLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=9ab9e6f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.storm.mg/lifestyle/1797528</a><br />\n<br />\n日本人討厭中國嗎？最新「全球態度調查」揭露世界各國對中國的看法，結果令人吃驚<br />\n中央社 <br />\n2019-10-07 09:49<br />\n<br />\n皮尤研究中心最新發布的「全球態度調查」顯示，中共10月1日慶祝建政70週年之際，在32個主要國家民眾，有41%對中國有好感，37%對中國持負面態度。其中，<strong>日本民眾對中國的看法最為負面</strong>，占比高達85%；2002年，日本民眾對中國表示好感的還有55%。<strong>對中國最有好感的國家是俄羅斯</strong>，該國民眾對中國持負面看法的僅有18%。<br />\n<br />\n皮尤研究中心（Pew Research Center）9月30日發布的調查顯示，中國在亞太地區的大多數鄰國獲得不利的評價。在日本，有85%的民眾對中國持負面態度；南韓以63%居次；澳洲（57%）和菲律賓（54%）持負面觀感的民眾也過半。<br />\n<br />\n皮尤指出，與去年相比，亞太國家受訪民眾對中國的好感都下滑，其中，印尼對中國的好感，從去年的53%，暴跌至現在的37%。在美國和加拿大，分別有60%和67%的人對中國持負面態度，且居於史上最高峰。<br />\n<br />\n皮尤指出，美國與中國的貿易緊張，使得美國民眾對中國的好感下降12%。中國華為公司首席財務官孟晚舟在加拿大被高調逮捕後，引發兩國關係緊張，促使加國民眾對中國的負評增加22%。<br />\n<br />\n在西歐地區，僅有希臘民眾對中國的好感過半（51%）。多數國家在這一年對中國持好感的比例下降兩位數，其中瑞典對中國持負評高達70%，好感度驟降17%；荷蘭也下降11%，英國下降10%。<br />\n<br />\n中歐和東歐分歧較大。保加利亞、波蘭人和立陶宛對中國的好感多於負面。相反的，許多斯洛伐克人和大多數捷克人對中國持負面看法。<br />\n<br />\n在所有接受調查的國家中，俄羅斯人對中國的看法最為積極（71%好感），比去年上升6%。接受調查的中東、拉丁美洲和撒哈拉以南非洲國家，多數人也對中國持好感。<br />\n<br />\n皮尤指出，這次是在2019年5月13日至8月29日對3萬4904人進行民調，儘管大多數國家的大多數人都同意，中國在世界舞台上的影響力已顯著增長，但調查顯示這並不一定轉化為對中國的好感。<br />\n<br />\n責任編輯／林安儒"},{"pid":"1c5581741e3763440112d511d2fdaafde89f42ba","tid":1649221,"uid":307203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:28:06.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n[品蔥建議] [拋磚引玉] 如何偽裝成一名合格的&ldquo;愛國港人&rdquo;（藍絲）？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648664</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fe819ccc1f00e3f9aab5b90b2733677c53a0640d","tid":1649221,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5727e519c328ad1871393f3a66a66a1624e239a7","tid":1649221,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:30:00.000Z","msg":"俄佬食花生"},{"pid":"346e8150306ef72730f27d7f107b1c70b78382cd","tid":1649221,"uid":259901,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:31:01.000Z","msg":"因為大陸人又有米又快手<br />\n班俄妹賺到笑，梗係中意大陸人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f4d7d68217175c403bef77154ad3374a5265c2a","tid":1649221,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:33:27.000Z","msg":"如果今日去美國做多次，正面既人會又少左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8586f0acab44e6c8db420aaf3265618367f9864","tid":1649221,"uid":326930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:36:36.000Z","msg":"我死黨係裝修判頭，佢話你知<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1649229\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1649229</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b11607840d7e4fa3b4dece65da334a21a07c86ff","tid":1649221,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:38:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840ab456a0891af71d9d0afda8e343fd4bdda085","tid":1649221,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:39:48.000Z","msg":"又係呢張 出過啦"},{"pid":"aed1c27ab2627783c6acafdf4b981d58cc93c4c5","tid":1649221,"uid":162095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:41:27.000Z","msg":"中國成日7出國際梗係啦<br />\n鍾意拎14億人黎打飛機<br />\n小氣又玻璃心"},{"pid":"57aab3d21cfa1446085fd5d2c1656df44730e61f","tid":1649221,"uid":18999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:42:25.000Z","msg":"有受歡迎過?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be3c72a4b609e3a77a70f09fcb5bcce0cc71516","tid":1649221,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"346e8150306ef72730f27d7f107b1c70b78382cd","tid":1649221,"uid":259901,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:31:01.000Z","msg":"因為大陸人又有米又快手<br />\n班俄妹賺到笑，梗係中意大陸人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:46:59.000Z","msg":"俄妹=雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf039d53ec47c15a5f4db3446adfcd1a989b456","tid":1649221,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:49:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37ea61400d4abafe194ce1dc31c68e497c2adb27","tid":1649221,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:51:36.000Z","msg":"呢個係咪早排有人po過出黎果個(?)<br />\n受訪日期2019年5月13日至8月29日,但國際局勢越黎越反共,家下真正民意應該比呢個調查對中國更反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aeebe2cd9de873fd38c0afa32f482297140a9ae","tid":1649221,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:52:15.000Z","msg":"成個海參威送畀你 緊受歡迎"},{"pid":"eb7928474021b98213f042c2ee7db16b2f2eccb1","tid":1649221,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:59:22.000Z","msg":"契弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9143a44f212b50a58e19bb6c7442cb532fee40b0","tid":1649221,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:00:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">全球「和尼畫」<br />\n#XinniethePooh Challenge</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t0UOaVn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft0UOaVn.png&h=c7fd48b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1yAhQxD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1yAhQxD.png&h=d230a326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「和尼畫」挑戰<br />\n1.畫出你心中所想的維尼圖<br />\n2.留下你想對習維尼講嘅說話<br />\n3.放上ig、fb、twitter，tag #XinniethePooh<br />\n4.tag 1-3個你想佢一齊畫維尼嘅朋友<br />\n5.被tag嘅朋友一齊畫維尼，讓愛與維尼佔領地球，推到畀習維尼本人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot; Challenge<br />\n1. Draw your own &quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot;<br />\n2. Write down what do you want to tell Chairman Xi<br />\n3. Post your work on ig, fb and twitter with tag #Xinniethepooh <br />\n4. Tag up to 3 more friends to draw together!<br />\n<br />\n更多作品：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23XinniethePooh&amp;src=typeahead_click\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3D%2523XinniethePooh%26src%3Dtypeahead_click&d=NX17wA0xajt0Xz52GN5L9goLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=68c999af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/search?q=%23XinniethePooh&amp;src=typeahead_click</a>"},{"pid":"f3104b0bb05b252d36babd0d7f698ba910168e9d","tid":1649221,"uid":155732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"346e8150306ef72730f27d7f107b1c70b78382cd","tid":1649221,"uid":259901,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:31:01.000Z","msg":"因為大陸人又有米又快手<br />\n班俄妹賺到笑，梗係中意大陸人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:12:36.000Z","msg":"快手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid